summary:
After around ten years of experience in all Human Resources professions in France, my personal life offered me the opportunity to live the expatriation. 
I have strengthened my ability to adapt, to be flexible and to understand the other (to adapt to an interlocutor from another culture / with a sensitivity different from its own). I am also perfectly able to interact in a multicultural and multilingual environment.
I now have a profile combining technical and managerial skills in human resources management, in the commercial sector and in communication and marketing.
